entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You recovered an important contact list detailing Rebel spies on Naboo.
entries.journal_entry_description: One of the Rebel spies operating on Naboo has been captured by the Empire. Travel to Naboo and recover his contact list before the Imperial troops have a chance to find it.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to Naboo and recover the contact list of a Rebel spy who has been detained by the Empire.
entries.task00_waypoint_name: Approximate location of the Imperial Base
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go to Moenia and give the recovered contact list to Bertos Goodner, the commander of the Rebel spies on Naboo. He is usually found near the starport in Moenia.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Meet with the Rebel Spy Commander
